<p><i><b>Madama Butterfly</b></i> (<i>Madame Butterfly</i>) is an <a href="/wiki/Opera" title="Opera">opera</a> in three acts (originally two acts) by <a href="/wiki/Giacomo_Puccini" title="Giacomo Puccini">Giacomo Puccini</a>, with an Italian <a href="/wiki/Libretto" title="Libretto">libretto</a> by <a href="/wiki/Luigi_Illica" title="Luigi Illica">Luigi Illica</a> and <a href="/wiki/Giuseppe_Giacosa" title="Giuseppe Giacosa">Giuseppe Giacosa</a>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
